metadata.name: CDB: LOST LEGENDS by loosetooth
metadata.description:
Lost amidst the chaos of the infamous evacuation of Gooch Island and only now re-exposing themselves to the world.

CDB: LOST LEGENDS are finding their way back to help rebuild the utopia of Gooch Island, the return is imminent.

14 unique LOST LEGENDARIES paying homage to the CryptoDickButt S3 collection.

Keep away from children.
